translations: adj.光荣的；可敬的；高贵的（honourable的美式写法）

phrs.translation: n. 优秀奖；鼓励奖；荣誉奖

sentences.sentence: Thou would'st not have an honorable Prince!
sentences.translation: 你是不会拥有一位尊贵的王子的！

sentences.sentence: Where I come from in southeast London, that's an honorable profession.
sentences.translation: 在我来自伦敦东南部的地方，这是一个光荣的职业。
